  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AnalyticsPageNameProvider
    Interface to be implemented by clients who want to provide their own logic for generating s.pageName for Analytics or retrieving Resources from custom pageName's.
    AnalyticsPageNameResolver
    The AnalyticsPageNameResolver service can be used to generate the Analytics pageName based on Framework mappings or other context data.
    ClassificationsService
    Provides methods for Analytics Classification API related calls as specified by the Classifications API.
    ClassificationsTransformer
    Is a specific interface extending Transformer for transforming resources in preparation for export as Classifications for Analytics.
    Filter
    Represents a variable filter for filtering out variables from the final result set.
